376
00:34:30,030 --> 00:34:35,450
It's a person called Ju Jae Il but it's the only one without an affiliation.

377
00:34:35,450 --> 00:34:37,700
I'll send you the address now.

378
00:34:37,700 --> 00:34:40,860
