381
00:34:57,710 --> 00:34:59,420
Who?

382
00:34:59,420 --> 00:35:02,110
Seoul Metropolitan Police Agency

383
00:35:08,370 --> 00:35:10,560
Seon Ho's friend?

384
00:35:10,560 --> 00:35:12,250
Yes.

385
00:35:12,250 --> 00:35:16,540
I'm sorry to say, but you can't meet him because he's being investigated.

386
00:35:18,050 --> 00:35:22,790
Then could I make one phone call to Seon Ho?

387
00:35:22,790 --> 00:35:25,310
Please.

388
00:35:35,100 --> 00:35:39,170
Not long, keep it short. And I have to listen in on it.

389
00:35:39,170 --> 00:35:41,040
Thank you.

390
00:36:16,680 --> 00:36:18,390
Kang Hui.

