00:37:11,980 --> 00:37:13,650
Feeling that way,

404
00:37:14,570 --> 00:37:17,090
I worried that something terrible happened to you.

405
00:37:18,560 --> 00:37:23,140
My heart would fall in an instant,

406
00:37:23,720 --> 00:37:28,060
I felt crazed worrying about the traffic,

407
00:37:28,060 --> 00:37:32,950
